<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">In the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Purchasing card reference number</strong> field, enter the reference number for the credit card. For example, enter the last four digits.</p>
<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">
