</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55">In the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55">Card holder name</strong> field, enter the cardholder's name as it appears on the purchasing card.</p>
