<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="57"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="57">Optional: In the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="57">Valid from</strong> field, enter the date when the card was issued to the employee.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58">Optional: In the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58">Expiry date</strong> field, enter the date when the card expires.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">Optional: In the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">Credit limit</strong> field, enter the maximum amount that can be charged to the card.</p>
