<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="82">Use this procedure to create a vendor invoice to record the periodic statement balance for a purchasing card statement that has been received from a purchasing card services provider.</p>
