</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="132"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="132">In the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="132">Lines</strong> grid area, select <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="132">Add line</strong>, and enter information about the line.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="133"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="133">To specify additional information about the line, select the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="133">Line details</strong> FastTab, and enter the information.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="134"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="134">Optional: Submit the invoice to the workflow system for review and approval, and then post the invoice.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="135"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="135">To save the invoice without posting it, close the page. You can view the invoice on the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/public-sector/purchasing-cards.md" sourcestartlinenumber="135">Pending vendor invoices</strong> list page.</p>
